title: Zeit Inch Nails 1/13: Supreme Court, Viagra, Texans, Jason Momoa, Kanye West, MGK

description:
In this edition of Zeit Inch Nails, Jack and Super Producer Becca discuss the Supreme Court blocking the vaccine mandate, alternative uses for Viagra, Jason Momoa and Lisa Bonet splitting up, Kanye West punching a fan, and MGK and Megan Fox getting engaged.
